data.title: Leslie Vincent: Amy Winehouse & Carole King @ Gnarly Bard Theater
data.meta_description: Leslie Vincent presents “Will You Still Love Me Tomorrow: An Evening of Amy Winehouse & Carole King.” Brimming with heartache and joy, this show celebrates the resilience of the human heart and the universal truths that Amy and Carole’s music both share. data.text:
Leslie Vincent presents “Will You Still Love Me Tomorrow: An Evening of Amy Winehouse & Carole King.” Brimming with heartache and joy, this show celebrates the resilience of the human heart and the universal truths that Amy and Carole’s music both share.

Featuring Ted Godbout on keys, Matt McIntyre on bass, Ben Ehrlich on drums, and Mitch Van Laar on trumpet, this show has been performed to sold-out crowds in St. Paul and continues to resonate with audience members of all ages.

"If you've seen or heard Leslie, you know what an incredible and unique voice she has” - Cherry and Spoon.
